quran[49]{c,v,t}:
  50,27,"Mugenzi we (Shitani) azavuga ati “Nyagasani wacu! Sinamuyobeje, ahubwo we yari mu buyobe buri kure (y’ukuri).”"
  50,28,(Allah azavuga ati) “Mwijya impaka imbere yanjye kandi narababuriye mbere (ko hazabaho) ibihano”
  50,29,"“Iwanjye ijambo ntirihindurwa, kandi sinjya mpuguza abagaragu banjye.”"
  50,30,Zirikana umunsi tuzabwira umuriro wa Jahanamu tuti “Ese wuzuye?” Maze uvuge uti “Ese hari inyongera (y’abandi ngo mubampe)?”
  50,31,Kandi ijuru rizegerezwa abagandukira Allah
  50,32,"(Bazabwirwa bati) “Iri (juru) ni ryo mwajyaga musezeranywa; (rigenewe) buri wese wicuza cyane kuri Allah, akanitwararika (ku mategeko ye)"
  50,33,"Wa wundi utinya Allah Nyirimpuhwe atamubona, ndetse akaza afite umutima wicuza"
  50,34,(Bazabwirwa bati) “Nimuryinjiremo (Ijuru) mu mahoro. Uyu ni umunsi w’ubuzima buzahoraho.”
  50,35,"Bazabonamo ibyo bashaka byose, kandi iwacu hari n’inyongera (yo kubona Allah imbonankubone)"
  50,36,"Ese ni ibisekuru bingahe tworetse mbere yabo, byabarushaga ubukana! Byari byarakwiriye mu bihugu byinshi bishaka ubuhungiro"
  50,37,"Mu by’ukuri muri ibyo harimo urwibutso k’ufite umutima, cyangwa uteze amatwi kandi akaba n’umuhamya (wita ku bintu)"
  50,38,"Rwose twaremye ibirere n’isi n’ibiri hagati yabyo mu minsi itandatu, kandi ntitwagize umunaniro"
  50,39,"Bityo, (yewe Muhamadi) jya wihanganira ibyo bavuga, unasingize ikuzo rya Nyagasani wawe mbere y’uko izuba rirasa na mbere y’uko rirenga"
  50,40,"Ndetse no mu ijoro ujye umusingiza, na nyuma yo kubama (nyuma y’iswala)"
  50,41,"Kandi uzatege amatwi umunsi uhamagara (Malayika uzavuza impanda), azahamagarira hafi"
  50,42,"Umunsi bazumva urusaku rw’impanda y’ukuri, uwo uzaba ari umunsi w’izuka"
  50,43,"Mu by’ukuri ni twe dutanga ubuzima tukanabwisubiza, kandi iwacu ni ho garukiro"
  50,44,"Umunsi isi izabasadukiraho, bakavamo bihuta. Uko kuzaba ari ukubakoranya koroshye kuri twe"
  50,45,Tuzi neza ibyo bavuga kandi wowe (Muhamadi) ntugomba kubahatira kwemera. Ahubwo wibutse wifashishije Qur’an wa wundi utinya ibihano byanjye
  51,1,"Ndahiye imiyaga ihuha cyane igatatanya (ibicu, ikazamura ivumbi, umusenyi n’ibindi)"
  51,2,N’ibyikoreye imitwaro (ibicu biremereye bitwara imvura)
  51,3,N’ibigenda mu buryo bworoshye (amato agenda mu nyanja)
  51,4,N’abashinzwe gukwirakwiza igeno (abamalayika)
  51,5,Mu by’ukuri ibyo musezeranywa (izuka n’ibindi bizaba ku munsi w’imperuka) ni impamo
  51,6,"Kandi rwose, kuzagororerwa (cyangwa guhanwa ku bakoze ibibi) bizabaho nta kabuza"
  51,7,Ndahiye ikirere kirimo amayira gikoze neza
  51,8,Rwose mufite imvugo zitandukanye (ku byerekeye intumwa Muhamadi ndetse n’iyi Qur’an)
  51,9,Uteshwa (gukurikira Qur’an n’intumwa Muhamadi) ni uwateshejwe (gukurikira ukuri)
  51,10,Abanyabinyoma baravumwe
  51,11,"Ba bandi bari mu bujiji, barangaye"
  51,12,Barabaza igihe umunsi w’ibihembo uzabera
  51,13,(Uzaba ari) umunsi bazaba bari mu muriro bahanwa
  51,14,(Bazabwirwa bati) “Ngaho nimwumve ibihano byanyu; ibi ni byo mwajyaga musaba ko byihutishwa.”
  51,15,Mu by’ukuri abagandukira Allah bazaba bari mu busitani n’amariba (yo mu Ijuru)
  51,16,Bakira ibyo Nyagasani wabo yabahaye. Mu by’ukuri mbere bari abakora ibyiza
  51,17,"Bajyaga baryama gake mu ijoro (kubera ko babaga basali, basingiza Nyagasani wabo)"
  51,18,No mu gicuku (mu rukerera babaga) basaba imbabazi (Allah)
  51,19,"No mu mitungo yabo, habagamo umugabane bagenera abakene basaba n’abihishira"
  51,20,No ku isi hari ibimenyetso ku bemera badashidikanya
  51,21,Ndetse no muri mwe ubwanyu (ibyo bimenyetso birimo). Ese ntimubona
  51,22,No mu kirere hari amafunguro yanyu ndetse n’ibyo musezeranywa
  51,23,"Bityo, ndahiye ku izina rya Nyagasani w’ikirere n’isi ko (ibyo musezeranywa) ari ukuri nko kuvuga kwanyu"
  51,24,Ese wamenye iby’inkuru y’abashyitsi ba Aburahamu b’abanyacyubahiro
  51,25,"Ubwo binjiraga iwe bakavuga bati “mugire amahoro (salamu!)” Nuko akavuga ati “Salamu, bantu batazwi.”"
  51,26,"Nuko arinyabya asanga ab’iwe, azana inyana ibyibushye (inyama z’inyana yokeje)"
  51,27,"Maze arazibegereza, (abonye batarambura amaboko ngo barye) aravuga ati “Ese nta bwo murya?”"
  51,28,Nuko arabishisha (abonye batariye). Baravuga bati “Humura!” Hanyuma bamuha inkuru nziza (yo kuzabyara umwana) w’umuhungu uzaba afite ubumenyi (ku bijyanye na Allah)
  51,29,"Nuko umugore we aza yiyamira, akubita agashyi mu buranga bwe (atangara), aravuga ati “Umukecuru w’urubereri!”"
  51,30,"Baravuga bati “Uko ni ko Nyagasani wawe yavuze. Mu by’ukuri ni Nyirubugenge buhambaye, Umumenyi uhebuje.”"